---
title: "Thank you"
description: "Your message is on its way — we'll reply within 24 hours."
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="container-x max-w-xl text-center">
    <p class="section-kicker">Got it!</p>
    <h1 class="section-title mb-4">Thank you — we'll be in touch.</h1>
    <p class="text-brand-off/70">
      Your message landed safely. We'll reply within 24 hours. If it's urgent,
      feel free to message us on WhatsApp.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center">
      <a href="/en/" class="btn-ghost">Back to home</a>
      <a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://wa.me/{{ site.whatsapp | replace('+','') }}" class="btn-primary">Open WhatsApp</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
